<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Megaman X2 on Rockman X3 PCB]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=10564&amp;p=119057#p119057"><![CDATA[
Mega Man X2 sets the Cx4 configuration differently than Mega Man X3. I don't recall the details. It's related to ROM configuration. I think X2 might use two MaskROMs. To use just one, you'd probably need to alter the ROM image to set the register for a single ROM chip.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1726">MottZilla</a> — Mon Oct 07, 2013 10:47 am</p><hr />
